latestPosts.caption:
My first Father’s Day without you feels so heavy Poppa.. 
Everywhere I look, people are sharing photos and stories with their dads—and it just makes me want to celebrate the day with you..
I find myself smiling at your photos one moment… and breaking down the next.
Grief is so strange ugh…. one minute I feel like I’m doing okay, and then out of nowhere something small reminds me of you, and it all comes crashing back.

You made me strong Poppa but today, I feel like your little Joja again… missing you so so so much ya 
I’d give anything for just one more hug from you. Just one… please!! 

You were my warrior.
My hero.
My first love.
My safe place.
My everything.

I love you forever, Poppa.
Happy Father’s Day ❤️‍🩹
Om Sai 🙏🏻
